ygData.subject: Hunting at LVL 35
ygData.msgSnippet: Hail good peoples of Norrath ! My name is Perriin and I am 36 ranger on the Karana server. Just curious to where people are hunting at this level.
ygData.messageBody:
Hail good peoples of Norrath ! <br>My name is
Perriin and I am 36 ranger on the Karana server.
<br><br>Just curious to where people are hunting at this
level. I have been hunting in OT, Mistymoore, and
Iceclad Ocean, hunting cougars.<br><br>I also wanted to
talk weapons. I use a wurmslayer as my primary, and BA
long sword in my secondary. Im always looking to get
bigger and better so im curious to what other people are
using. Any suggestions on what do buy ? Im primarily a
1HSlasher. Im leaning toward weapons that have smaller dly
rather than dmg. <br><br>Your thoughts )
